---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Construction Drone Services Colorado | Wet Dog Drones">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mb-6">
        The 1 AM Drone Pilot Keeping Colorado Construction Projects on Track
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        My day starts at 1:00 a.m. While you're sleeping, I'm answering emails, processing data, and preparing flight plans for Colorado construction sites. By the time most people wake up, I've already put in four hours on Wet Dog Drones.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-8">
        Then I commute 64 miles to my day job — which happens to be with my biggest client.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href="/services" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition text-lg">
          See How We Save Projects Money
        </a>
        <a href="/case-studies" class="border border-white text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-white hover:text-slate-900 transition text-lg">
          View Case Studies
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Truth Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-amber-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-800">
        "Getting your Part 107 doesn't give you a license to print money. That's the lie we were all sold."
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600">
        The money's out there. But you've got to chase it. You've got to show up. And you've got to be willing to grind for three years before it clicks.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services Section -->
  <section class="py-20" id="services">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Construction Progression Monitoring That Pays for Itself</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">Decision-grade data, 24–48 hour turnaround, Procore-compatible deliverables.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Service 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">📅</span> Bi-Weekly Progress Flights
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Baseline before anyone steps on site. Return every two weeks with orthomosaics, 3D models, and timeline comparisons. Scale back to monthly after dry-in.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">📸</span> Pre-Construction Documentation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Road damage, interior fixtures, site conditions — all timestamped and georeferenced. When change orders come, you have proof of what was actually there.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 3 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">🏢</span> Interior Documentation
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">84,000 square feet. 20 hours on site. Every fixture, every radiator, every piece of copper — mapped and documented before construction crews arrive.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Service 4 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">📊</span> Volumetric Surveys & 3D Modeling
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Cut/fill calculations, stockpile measurements, BIM-ready point clouds. Compatible with Procore, Autodesk, and your VDC workflow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a href="/services" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800 transition">View Full Services →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- By The Numbers -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">By The Numbers — What Three Years of Grinding Looks Like</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400">1:00 AM</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Day Starts</div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400">6</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Days/Week</div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400">3</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Years Grinding</div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400">$7K</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Startup Investment</div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-400">$30K</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Part-time Revenue</div>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center p-6 bg-slate-800 rounded-xl">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-400">$440K+</div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">Client Savings</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case Studies -->
  <section class="py-20" id="case-studies">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Real Projects. Real Dollars Saved.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Case Study 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600 to-blue-800 h-48 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-6xl">🏛️</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">$40,000 SAVED</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Severance Library</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Pre-construction baseline documentation proved existing road damage before construction began. Split an $80K change order.</p>
            <a href="/case-studies/severance-library" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800 transition">Read the Story →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Case Study 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-600 to-amber-800 h-48 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-6xl">🏫</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">$400,000 SAVED</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Clear Creek Schools</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Interior documentation proved building was empty when copper went missing. GC ate the $400K change order.</p>
            <a href="/case-studies/clear-creek-schools" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800 transition">Read the Story →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Case Study 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-600 to-slate-800 h-48 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-6xl">🏗️</span>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="text-blue-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">16 MONTHS</div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">The $58 Million Project</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">14 months of progress compressed into an 85-second time-lapse. Bi-weekly flights through closeout.</p>
            <a href="/case-studies/severmore-project" class="text-blue-600 font-semibold hover:text-blue-800 transition">See the Timeline →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">From Flight to Data in 24–48 Hours</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Mission Planning</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Coordinate with your superintendent, check airspace, plan flight paths. Class D waivers when needed.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Data Collection</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Part 107 certified pilots. All PPE, safety protocols, FAA compliance. NOTAMs and LAANC on us.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Processing & Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Ortho maps, 3D point clouds, timeline comparisons. Procore, Autodesk, and BIM compatible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Protect Your Project?</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
        Every project over $5M needs documentation before the first shovel hits dirt. Don't wait for the change order to wish you had proof.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition text-lg inline-block">
        Get a Quote for Your Project
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
